<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I didnt read all the posts, If u want help my best suggestion is a few tips on soloing. it can be rememberd very simply. (u gota be at least level 22 to try this though) Tank, root heal, repeat. Basically u tank the mob root him an get back a few steps and heal urself. Now never underestimate flash of light. It is a fear spell if u use it properly. If u ever gota run cast this spell take a step back an watch the mob run away heh. Also try to train 2hs early, ur gona be using it later. It will make a dif in dmg u deal. now as for pally taking dmg an dealing. at 45 i could outdeal some mnks wars rogs etc in dmg. Arb combine greatsword and a fbss) save up and camp taht fbss to hell lol. soulfire isnt worth using anymore ( hopefully i get Fa soon anyhow. just a few tips enjoy.   And this is a very underestimated class. My best frend in RL plays a war i dueld him at 40 an kicked his ass, an he has great kunark/velious gear. then he saw me kill a 41 twnk monk when i was 40 the same week. (the mnk actually cheated an got his frend to come to arena and blind me a few times lol) anyhow show us off and remember pride. You are a paladin, a holy knight, defender of truth. <p>

